Name: Boxed Out
About the game: Minimalist vibrant palettes and challenging puzzles. Features: Stimulating puzzle design: Easy to get, but difficult to master. Minimalist design: Only the barest elements without losing its essential purpose and identity. Teleportation: Teleportation levels increases the complexity of the puzzles, making them more challenging. 50+ Levels
